[13.412478, "o", "\u001b[22;1H\u001b[38;5;239m\u001b[48;5;237m\u276f \u001b[38;5;231mAdd one short joke about credentials to jokes.md, then commit it, push it, and open a pull request. This is issue #221.\u001b[39m                                       \u001b[27;1H\u001b[49m\u001b[38;5;174m\u2736\u001b[CScampering\u2026 \u001b[30;1H\u001b[38;5;246m\u276f\u00a0\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[32;51H\u001b[38;5;246mesc to interrupt \u00b7 \u2190 for agents\u001b[30;3H\u001b[m\u000f"]
